<br>
If you're referring to the change in recast time of Grim Aura...<br>
<br>
I don't believe there will be any change to how the item itself works, but only if you're casting the spell from your spell bar. From my experience, recast times do not apply to right clicks on items.<br>
<br>
An example that I can think of is the Temple of Sol Ro quest for the Earthen Boots. Earthen Boots have &quot;Invisibility vs. Animals&quot; as an instant right click effect. According to Lucy, the spell has a 6 second recast time. However, if you use the Earthen Boots, there is no delay needed between each click. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=60465">Xerphanis</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Arch Convoker</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=wildet>Wildet </A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 200<br> <font color=#333333>(1/14/03 6:50:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=408.topic&index=78>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: ...</span><hr size=1> Ah Noonie.. the vitrolic mage of &quot;I know better than anyone else therefore I will belittle everyone cause it makes me feel like I am worth anything&quot;<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
